title: Crossfire and Rainbow (Eclipse Comics)
description:
'Crossfire and Rainbow' is up next in the Eclipse Comics Upload Project!

Remember that Crossfire dude from the previous upload? And that Rainbow chick from DNA Agents? Yeah, it's them. This is a four-issue mini published by Eclipse in 1986, written and illustrated by the Crossfire team of Evanier and Spiegle.

As usual, praise to the creators and the scanners! Get you it, seed you it!
